snippet.title: Intelligence Trader
snippet.description: In Intelligence Trader you'll become the head of the secret organization of spies and information merchants. Plunge into the atmosphere of the Cold War, track the way of the famous confrontation, from the Berlin crisis to the Charter of Paris, and try to influence the course of history!
